= Vocabulary
== Purpose of the Document
Define basic terms and definitions.

== Vocabulary
.Vocabulary
[%autowidth, options="header"]
|===
|Term | Description

|User
|Anyone who seeks for a job

|Vacancy
|Interesting for user vacancy

|Job applcation
|The process of of competition for a job

|Stage
|The stage of job application process

|CV
|User's CV that was sent to apply to a vacancy

|Message
|Text or file with information about job application

|Employer
|A company which placed the vacancy

|Job offer
|A job offer was got by user from emploer

|Human Resources Manager (HRManager)
|Someone who represents an emoployer

|Job searching proccess
|The process of seeking for a new job. Can consist of multiple vacancies.

|===